### Health check
GET http://localhost:3001/api/health

### Transcribe audio
POST http://localhost:3001/api/analyze-audio/transcribe
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary123

--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="test.webm"
Content-Type: audio/webm

< ./path/to/your/audio.webm
--boundary123--

### Extract marks from text
POST http://localhost:3001/api/analyze-audio/extract
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Habibul got 19, 2336 got 17",
  "dataset": [
    {"id": "259-12-33-2", "name": "Habibul"},
    {"id": "259-12-33-6", "name": "Tushar"}
  ]
}